description.narrative:
This Project is expected to have high development impact with significant social and economic benefits:
(i) supporting one of the leading private banks in the market by investing in the bank's first mortgage covered bond issued in local currency;
(ii) improving access to housing finance to Turkey's young and fast growing population, where market penetration remains quite low with a residential mortgage loan-to-GDP ratio of 7.3 percent as of year-end 2015;
(iii) increasing the share of green mortgages in the market; and
(iv) continuing to help develop Turkey's capital markets through the issuance of a new instrumentâ?the country's first mortgage covered bond issuance in local currency.
